"client refreshes every time a user connects to a different app server. "
"This occurs because the servers have different ``config.json`` files in a"
" high availability cluster-based deployment."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/scale/high-availability-cluster-based-deployment.rst:631
msgid ""
